---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
---

<Layout
  title="Private AI Infrastructure"
  description="Keep AI in your own cloud with fixed pricing, compliance-ready guardrails, and a 48-hour rollout."
>
  <SiteNav />

  <main class="bg-zinc-900">
    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 mb-4">
            private ai for enterprises
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">
            Your AI. Your data. Your control.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Launch a ChatGPT-style experience that runs entirely inside your infrastructure. No per-seat
            pricing, no mystery data trails—just fast, private AI your team actually trusts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-4">Why cloud AI falls short</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
              Public tools like ChatGPT or Claude are incredible, but they open up three headaches for
              operators handling sensitive data.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-red-400"></span>
                <span><strong>Data privacy:</strong> Every prompt leaves your environment and lives on somebody else’s servers.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-red-400"></span>
                <span><strong>Compliance risk:</strong> HIPAA, SOC 2, and privilege requirements all hinge on keeping records in-house.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-red-400"></span>
                <span><strong>Total cost:</strong> $60+ per user adds up fast when every seat needs access.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-4">Side-by-side snapshot</h3>
            <table class="w-full text-sm text-left text-zinc-300">
              <thead>
                <tr class="text-zinc-400 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">
                  <th class="py-2">Cloud AI</th>
                  <th class="py-2">Your Private AI</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-t border-zinc-800">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Data on vendor servers</td>
                  <td class="py-3">Data never leaves your network</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-zinc-800">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">$60/user/month</td>
                  <td class="py-3">$3k/month, unlimited users</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-zinc-800">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Forced updates + terms</td>
                  <td class="py-3">You decide when models change</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-zinc-800">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Limited customization</td>
                  <td class="py-3">Full control over prompts + policies</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-12">Simple pricing that scales with trust</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-2">Professional Package</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">Best for teams getting started with private AI.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Starting at $8,000 one-time</span> — infrastructure deployment, 3 models, team training</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Starting at $3,000/month</span> — hosting, monitoring, support, unlimited users</li>
              <li>Includes onboarding playbooks and documentation handoff</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-2">Enterprise Package</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-4">For organizations that need deeper integrations and oversight.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Starting at $15,000 one-time</span> — custom integrations, fine-tuning, extended onboarding</li>
              <li><span class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Starting at $5,000/month</span> — priority support, dedicated optimization</li>
              <li>Includes compliance documentation and change management playbooks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-zinc-950 border-b border-zinc-800/60">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-6">What’s included</h2>
            <div class="grid gap-4">
              <a
                href="/infrastructure"
                class="card-slate block transition-smooth hover:border-zinc-600 group"
              >
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2 group-hover:text-zinc-50">
                  Infrastructure
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Runs in your cloud account (GCP, AWS, or Azure) with enterprise GPUs, auto-scaling,
                  and 99.9% uptime SLA.
                </p>
                <span class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-200 group-hover:text-zinc-50 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                  Learn how we deploy infrastructure
                  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="/learn/models"
                class="card-slate block transition-smooth hover:border-zinc-600 group"
              >
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2 group-hover:text-zinc-50">
                  AI models (model-agnostic)
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Deploy Claude, OpenAI, Gemini, Llama, Mistral, Qwen, fine-tunes, or local models. Pick what fits your policy, latency, and cost requirements. Switch anytime without rebuilding.
                </p>
                <span class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-200 group-hover:text-zinc-50 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                  See model-agnostic delivery
                  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="/applications"
                class="card-slate block transition-smooth hover:border-zinc-600 group"
              >
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2 group-hover:text-zinc-50">
                  Applications
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Web app, mobile apps, Office add-ins, and open APIs so your workflows stay seamless.
                </p>
                <span class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-200 group-hover:text-zinc-50 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                  See the application playbook
                  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="/security-compliance"
                class="card-slate block transition-smooth hover:border-zinc-600 group"
              >
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2 group-hover:text-zinc-50">
                  Security &amp; compliance
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  Encryption, RBAC, audit logging, HIPAA/SOC2 readiness, and data residency controls.
                </p>
                <span class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-200 group-hover:text-zinc-50 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                  Review security and compliance guardrails
                  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="/support"
                class="card-slate block transition-smooth hover:border-zinc-600 group"
              >
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2 group-hover:text-zinc-50">
                  Support
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                  White-glove onboarding, 24/7 monitoring, 4-hour response SLA (1-hour for enterprise),
                  and monthly optimization reviews.
                </p>
                <span class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-200 group-hover:text-zinc-50 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                  Understand the support program
                  <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-2">Example scopes & pain points</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
                <li><strong>Healthcare practice · Birmingham, AL:</strong> Needed HIPAA-safe chat over treatment guidelines; we deployed a private portal with audit trails.</li>
                <li><strong>Law firm · Gulf Shores, AL:</strong> Required privileged research assistant; we configured secure document retrieval with approval checkpoints.</li>
                <li><strong>CPA firm · Mobile, AL:</strong> Sought faster workpaper summaries; we delivered a restricted agent that drafts memos from internal records.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-2">48-hour launch plan</h3>
              <ol class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300 list-decimal list-inside">
                <li>Kickoff call (30 minutes)</li>
                <li>Infrastructure deployed</li>
                <li>Models installed & tested</li>
                <li>Team training session</li>
                <li>Go live with support</li>
              </ol>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-3">
                Recent deployments have gone live within two to five business days, depending on data integrations and reviews.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-lg p-5 border border-zinc-700">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Security-first data flow</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-2">
                Cloud AI: <span class="text-zinc-100">User → Internet → Vendor → Training Data → Response</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Private AI: <span class="text-zinc-100">User → Your Network → Response</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-2">Zero external transmission. Ever.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-50 mb-4">Common questions</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Can we customize it?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Absolutely. Bring your industry prompts, templates, or tools—everything plugs into the platform.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">What if intent solutions io disappears?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">You own the infrastructure inside your account. If we vanish, your system keeps running.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">How do you handle compliance?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">We deliver HIPAA/SOC2-ready documentation, BAAs, audit trails, and retention policies.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Can we integrate it?</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Yes—connect via API to your EHR, CRM, accounting suite, or homegrown tools.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-slate space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-3">Ready to get started?</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-300 mb-4">
                Book a 15-minute demo and we’ll tailor the proposal to your team size, compliance needs,
                and model preferences.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                <li>📧 <a href="mailto:jeremy@intentsolutions.io" class="hover:text-zinc-200 transition-smooth">jeremy@intentsolutions.io</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-3">About intent solutions io</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
                Jeremy Longshore brings 20 years of operations experience plus AI automation expertise. We ship
                production systems in days—not months—and support every build right here in Gulf Shores.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
